	<string># Ghostty Runner

**Version:** 0.1.0  
**Author:** islgl(hi@lglgl.cc)

Run commands directly in Ghostty terminal via Alfred.

## Usage

Type `&gt;` followed by your command:

```bash
ls -la
git status
npm install
```

## Requirements

- macOS
- Ghostty terminal installed
- Alfred Powerpack

## Notes

- Commands are executed in a new Ghostty window
- Shell remains open after execution
- Supports commands with spaces and arguments</string>
